         <abstract id="aspace_d2633d70537e923992985ab71f94f841">The collection contains photographs documenting the construction of the Hall of Graduate Studies at Yale. Included are interior and exterior views.</abstract>
    
      </did>
      <odd id="aspace_cac130e7468f165be87d251fe8d807c8">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 46-B (YRG 46-B), Records and materials documenting individual Yale buildings, facilities, and grounds.</p>  
      </odd>
      <prefercite id="aspace_0a3a8f2225ca1e0695c5582d87370c69">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Hall of Graduate Studies, Yale University, Photographs (RU 623). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_c6e1ef8db965554a773e6eb671f223c1">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>The materials are open for research.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <arrangement id="aspace_35602289f03c16cd60821fc7325b645a">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The materials are arranged in three series: I. Construction Progress Photographs, 1930-1932. II. General Views, 1932-1979. III. Oversize, slides, and transparencies.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_83149e972330b10544e25e86968e1c30">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection contains photographs documenting the construction of the Hall of Graduate Studies at Yale. Included are interior and exterior views.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
